Package net.xeoh.plugins.base.annotations.events

Annoations related to plugin events.

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Init
    Use this annotation to mark functions which should be called on initialization.
    PluginLoaded
    Called when a plugin of the given interface was registered.
    Shutdown
    Methods marked with this interface will be called on the shutdown of the PluginManager.
